Sure it sucks to be kicked from the clearnet, but this is kinda like a return to the basics, you know? To when we posted on bulletin boards and darknet forums that you needed to know how to access, before Jewgle started indexing everything.

I mean, 90s nostalgia is a thing among the normalfags, maybe it's good to get in our version of that bandwagon as well.
